<p>游览了<strong>天游峰、虎啸岩、</strong><strong>一线天</strong>等景区</p>
<p>观看了实景演出《印象大红袍》</p>
<p><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201031/e1ade41a5aa946608bc475fb9148d27e.jpeg" /></p>
<p>这趟高铁旅游专列</p>
<p>为<strong>双休日开行</strong></p>
<p>拉近了省会福州与武夷山的距离</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
